{"name":"Background: Soldier: Ideal","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Soldier","keys":["d6","Ideal"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Greater Good.</b> Our lot is to lay down our lives in defense of others. (Good)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"iG54mTaNWT1dxYcd"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Responsibility.</b> I do what I must and obey just authority. (Lawful)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"XGPSVWzsHcBQWJNT"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Independence.</b> When people follow orders blindly, they embrace a kind of tyranny. (Chaotic)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"sgEj9DVDXWJUNrBU"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Might.</b> In life as in war, the stronger force wins. (Evil)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"lAS1DMdgNeLudmA9"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Live and Let Live.</b> Ideals aren’t worth killing over or going to war for. (Neutral)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"4pEBGEWSnasHDDfl"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Nation.</b> My city, nation, or people are all that matter. (Any)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Mf8mNkVgNKDEWKue"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686318697369,"modifiedTime":1686318697369,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"2FauFJLKDmhJURnT"}
{"name":"Background: Sage: Ideal","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Sage","keys":["d6","Ideal"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Knowledge.</b> The path to power and self-improvement is through knowledge. (Neutral)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"jv9RwYe1IfX2aJu3"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Beauty.</b> What is beautiful points us beyond itself toward what is true. (Good)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"7Id7D5s9cWRjQBpA"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Logic.</b> Emotions must not cloud our logical thinking. (Lawful)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"TW2aDmvak8ACz2Zj"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>No Limits.</b> Nothing should fetter the infinite possibility inherent in all existence. (Chaotic)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"l9XCYmFL7tKmVQMC"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Power.</b> Knowledge is the path to power and domination. (Evil)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"dP8VPqvwQLWDy94j"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>Self-Improvement.</b> The goal of a life of study is the betterment of oneself. (Any)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Yf7lvQwRY7AbY7dG"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381686533,"modifiedTime":1692381686533,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"FLIKPk54JMlQojsA"}
{"name":"Background: Sage: Personality Trait","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Sage","keys":["d8","Personality Trait"],"diceKeys":["d8"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I use polysyllabic words that convey the impression of great erudition.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"1fQwODVSwijuLHEz"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’ve read every book in the world’s greatest libraries—or I like to boast that I have.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"uI1lRwyf4itONC5e"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m used to helping out those who aren’t as smart as I am, and I patiently explain anything and everything to others.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"dQ4pYmgmBabSBxGn"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"There’s nothing I like more than a good mystery.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"irSuIiwqAylxk1QD"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m willing to listen to every side of an argument before I make my own judgment.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Y6n7kTJ6a0MIvJ9A"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I … speak … slowly … when talking … to idiots, … which … almost … everyone … is … compared … to me.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"q2CRNemuGHMUC0JE"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I am horribly, horribly awkward in social situations.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"zRAduxUCjjVM7AlK"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m convinced that people are always trying to steal my secrets.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"GD5hBe6colkcZkq2"}],"formula":"d8","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381686525,"modifiedTime":1692381686525,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"Q8R99jlbdoxkYaa3"}
{"name":"Background: Soldier: Flaw","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Soldier","keys":["d6","Flaw"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The monstrous enemy we faced in battle still leaves me quivering with fear.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"7fuD9XrUazND7I3s"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I have little respect for anyone who is not a proven warrior.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"F8ZwwQ5motHJDqV8"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I made a terrible mistake in battle that cost many lives—and I would do anything to keep that mistake secret.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"hSdMgSYLMzd4t6U9"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"My hatred of my enemies is blind and unreasoning.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"E8nABjD12VNMOBqE"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I obey the law, even if the law causes misery.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"JGktXskmXrQmqcWd"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’d rather eat my armor than admit when I’m wrong.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"ZvIpE040DuSgqWGi"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686318697383,"modifiedTime":1686318697383,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"TTAs9OPGx1iKjUsb"}
{"name":"Background: Soldier: Personality Trait","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Soldier","keys":["d8","Personality Trait"],"diceKeys":["d8"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m always polite and respectful.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"pAt3Yt3WHLVdfEZq"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m haunted by memories of war. I can’t get the images of violence out of my mind.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"ZwKRuzn4ZKB9i6aA"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’ve lost too many friends, and I’m slow to make new ones.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"wO3Phgocx5bbRLGM"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’m full of inspiring and cautionary tales from my military experience relevant to almost every combat situation.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"456cCb06p2LDjQT7"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I can stare down a hell hound without flinching.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"FWLWKOLGrIHZZfsr"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I enjoy being strong and like breaking things.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"rvRrOTmQVSJ7atdx"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I have a crude sense of humor.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"TBbKtlVAHm0oM59H"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I face problems head-on. A simple, direct solution is the best path to success.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"7bbGP8VTPij7vWAq"}],"formula":"d8","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686318697362,"modifiedTime":1686318697362,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"TvZJLvaMHXyYrBFS"}
{"name":"Background: Sage: Flaw","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Sage","keys":["d6","Flaw"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I am easily distracted by the promise of information.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"6PPkIUDcsHhTiZia"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Most people scream and run when they see a demon. I stop and take notes on its anatomy.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"IUFc8oLdNmSeCYrR"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Unlocking an ancient mystery is worth the price of a civilization.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"rZOBrB01ZCQlGrFd"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I overlook obvious solutions in favor of complicated ones.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"WSERqhVrpBKUGrKo"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I speak without really thinking through my words, invariably insulting others.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Qn3LLGuRL8PBVcQr"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I can’t keep a secret to save my life, or anyone else’s.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"VG61MpNAVdNf2qEC"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381686546,"modifiedTime":1692381686546,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"dLBOnX5ayIKl2kxM"}
{"name":"Background: Hermit: Life of Seclusion","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Hermit","keys":["d8","Life of Seclusion"],"diceKeys":["d8"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I was searching for spiritual enlightenment.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"ld51PChHAG1JzT3U"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I was partaking of communal living in accordance with the dictates of a religious order.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"JIctxK5pgTgnYAG3"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I was exiled for a crime I didn’t commit.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"VzXW4K85QGEkSBV1"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I retreated from society after a life-altering event.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"WgATVfV8i83ppdq6"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I needed a quiet place to work on my art, literature, music, or manifesto.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"YDjccTbhnNmdE9v2"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I needed to commune with @Compendium[dnd5e.rules.0AGfrwZRzSG0vNKb]{nature}, far from civilization.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"7mPPnqU1JpCM85Sa"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I was the caretaker of an ancient ruin or relic.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"6HviBOFzjBqNqNoe"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I was a pilgrim in search of a person, place, or relic of spiritual significance.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"DmIDddc7cE0Z4DNk"}],"formula":"d8","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381786569,"modifiedTime":1692381786569,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"iIy4Escm2jSorAAP"}
{"name":"Background: Sage: Specialty","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Sage","keys":["d8","Specialty"],"diceKeys":["d8"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Alchemist","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"bpvPu6fJ7NghivZq"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Astronomer","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"eWKuiapU2XUPkZuy"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Discredited academic","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"KqEOHSOrDEGSAfXv"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Librarian","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Oqq7lednv5vnElDW"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Professor","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"nNgWblaY6ihYvbtp"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Researcher","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"y7qGGbCigsZC6HVq"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Wizard’s apprentice","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"QAacp9YAjR7fZMTl"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Scribe","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"OvAOgN9eVsKoUwu8"}],"formula":"d8","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381686513,"modifiedTime":1692381686513,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"jtfjxyoXnKVwpozV"}
{"name":"Background: Soldier: Bond","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Soldier","keys":["d6","Bond"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I would still lay down my life for the people I served with.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"6aTuFJbycHTwYxFi"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Someone saved my life on the battlefield. To this day, I will never leave a friend behind.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"vOSaK6htmwUgRBaV"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"My honor is my life.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"kyr5f8gfuL5GAkp7"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’ll never forget the crushing defeat my company suffered or the enemies who dealt it.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"UL8JCyQkASumvWXB"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Those who fight beside me are those worth dying for.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"C7f0XGvkersXr5SL"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I fight for those who cannot fight for themselves.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"d5koZ6rm9IgqMrJG"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686318697377,"modifiedTime":1686318697377,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"kCC127DPDVCrdW3Z"}
{"name":"Background: Soldier: Specialty","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Soldier","keys":["d8","Specialty"],"diceKeys":["d8"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Officer","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"guHSSzugcuSazMrP"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Scout","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"aOQVtpINRiSO0omc"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Infantry","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"MOl5jKwcmuyGSMb5"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Cavalry","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"j8M9rp9VfXpBONAH"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Healer","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"nVJTWOAipYUL0KDf"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Quartermaster","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"AjetaBtsEawZGyzy"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Standard bearer","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"AU5PNUahDO06OxQX"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Support staff (cook, blacksmith, or the like)","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"gbXufRju2oVN2faZ"}],"formula":"d8","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686318697350,"modifiedTime":1686318697350,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"oLuQBW3qBCxgNgAl"}
{"name":"Background: Sage: Bond","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Background: Sage","keys":["d6","Bond"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"It is my duty to protect my students.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"w3JY9MkygYTplAKH"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I have an ancient text that holds terrible secrets that must not fall into the wrong hands.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"JEBABWj0eXMUT9zd"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I work to preserve a library, university, scriptorium, or monastery.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"gMyvh78GUB2YkxV1"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"My life’s work is a series of tomes related to a specific field of lore.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"OsvtAPfgPvLi0noN"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I’ve been searching my whole life for the answer to a certain question.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"mNXMU30eezAW7uzS"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"I sold my soul for knowledge. I hope to do great deeds and win it back.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"9kYsAUmB5ueNMGhe"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692381686540,"modifiedTime":1692381686540,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_id":"orfiM5gf164gR4yL"}
